  "title": "Trade Analyst (Foreign Exchange) (No Experience Needed)",
  "description": "<p><strong>about the company</strong></p><p>Our client is a leading global private bank and is the key division of a premier international financial group.</p><p><strong>about the job</strong></p><ul><li>Accurately book FX trades into Wealth Management and Global Market systems.</li><li>Proactively notify the Front Office and Operations teams once new FX trades are booked.</li><li>Manage the end-to-end lifecycle for FX Accumulators and Structures. This includes generating fixing notifications, informing the Front Office of outcomes, and booking those outcomes into the relevant systems.</li><li>Generate and upload Money Market rates to systems.</li><li>Generate and export Fixed Income Pricing to the Access Database to facilitate Front Office recommendations.<br /></li></ul><p><strong>skills and experience required</strong></p><ul><li>Familiar with FX markets and products (especially Options and Accumulators)</li><li>Proficient at MS VBA, Excel, Access</li><li>Attention to detail</li><li>Great communication skills</li><li>A good team player<br /></li></ul><p>To apply online please use the 'apply' function.</p><p>(EA: 94C3609/ R24124496)</p>",
